description:
Danny recaps this week's The Real Housewives of Beverly Hills, which featured the women talking about ages and dating, a spa day, Christmas decor shopping, Dorit's new artwork, Portia's surprise, and lots more! Danny also dives into the new Halloween movie trailer starring Kyle "The Splits" Richards!
